        <num>9-12-4</num>
        <content>
          <p>Verdicts shall have a reasonable intendment and shall receive a reasonable construction. They shall not be avoided unless from necessity.</p>
          <p>(Orig. Code 1863, § 3481; Code 1868, § 3503; Code 1873, § 3561; Code 1882, § 3561; Civil Code 1895, § 5332; Civil Code 1910, § 5927; Code 1933, § 110-105.)</p>
